  ('social-worker-moex-02541', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-104-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '方案及服務活動必須與預算相結合，且須同時考量方案的直接支出與間接支出，這種預算類型稱為：', '["零基預算（zero-based budgeting）", "逐項預算（line-item budgeting）", "方案預算（program budgeting）", "功能預算（functional budgeting）"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:13+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7528bca53179", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6a2111ca5bab", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "104030", "c": "110", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "104", "exam_name": "104年第一次專技醫師中醫師分階段考試、中醫師營養師心理師護理師社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 17, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02542', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-104-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列那一項機構層面的因素最容易造成社會工作人員成為案主暴力攻擊的對象？', '["社會工作人員的輕忽", "預算緊縮、人力不足", "案主酗酒或失業", "社會工作人員的溝通技巧不佳"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:13+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7528bca53179", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6a2111ca5bab", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "104030", "c": "110", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "104", "exam_name": "104年第一次專技醫師中醫師分階段考試、中醫師營養師心理師護理師社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 18, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02543', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-104-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '1990 年代，企業界引用職場靈性（workplace spirituality）的概念，希望透過靈性管理協助員工找回工作 的意義，提升工作士氣和生產力。請問倡導職場靈性的管理學先驅是下列何者？', '["弗德利克泰勒（Frederick W. Taylor）", "彼得杜拉克（Peter Drucker）", "瑪莉芙麗特（Mary P. Follett）", "瑪莉芮奇孟（Mary Richmond）"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:13+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7528bca53179", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6a2111ca5bab", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "104030", "c": "110", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "104", "exam_name": "104年第一次專技醫師中醫師分階段考試、中醫師營養師心理師護理師社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 19, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02544', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-104-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '依據志願服務法第9條規定，志願服務運用單位應對志工辦理基礎訓練、特殊訓練。其中，內政部90年 9月14日（90）內中社字第9072501號函頒的社會福利志工特殊訓練課程，有一門必修課程是下列何者？', '["志願服務發展趨勢", "社會資源與志願服務", "志工督導技巧", "志願服務方案設計"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:13+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7528bca53179", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6a2111ca5bab", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "104030", "c": "110", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "104", "exam_name": "104年第一次專技醫師中醫師分階段考試、中醫師營養師心理師護理師社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 20, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02545', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-104-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '對於長期投入社會住宅倡導運動的志工而言，下列那一種觀點最適合說明其所投入的志願服務工作？', '["慈善服務的觀點", "公民社會的觀點", "文化休閒的觀點", "優勢條件的觀點"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:13+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7528bca53179", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6a2111ca5bab", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "104030", "c": "110", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "104", "exam_name": "104年第一次專技醫師中醫師分階段考試、中醫師營養師心理師護理師社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 21, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02546', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-104-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '在系統理論中，開放系統（open systems）的管理者為確保組織各部分彼此協調，而在不同的情況下， 以不同的方法，同樣有效地達到組織所預期的目標。這種特性最適合稱為下列何者？', '["殊途同歸性（equifinality）", "分化（differentiation）", "負熵（negative entropy）", "回饋（feedback）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:13+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7528bca53179", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6a2111ca5bab", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "104030", "c": "110", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "104", "exam_name": "104年第一次專技醫師中醫師分階段考試、中醫師營養師心理師護理師社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 22, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02547', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-104-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', 'Thomas（1991）撰寫《超越種族與性別》（Beyond Race and Gender），認為一個組織在多元性（diversity） 的管理中，第一個層次的改變是讓少數族群及女性有機會進入職場。這一個層次稱為下列何者？', '["肯定行動（affirmative action）", "重視差異（valuing difference）", "管理多元（managing diversity）", "文化熟練（cultural proficiency）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:13+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7528bca53179", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6a2111ca5bab", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "104030", "c": "110", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "104", "exam_name": "104年第一次專技醫師中醫師分階段考試、中醫師營養師心理師護理師社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 23, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02548', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-104-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '社會工作管理者若具有脈絡敏感度，能關注個人的特殊性與社會環境的差異性，則更能肯定性別、種族、 階級、國籍、宗教、性傾向與能力所存在的差異，並重視差異的分配式正義。這最適合下列那一種理論 的觀點？', '["新管理主義（neo-manageralism）", "Z理論（Z theory）", "女性主義關懷倫理（feminist ethics of care）", "新韋伯國家論（neo-Weberian State）"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:13+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7528bca53179", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6a2111ca5bab", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "104030", "c": "110", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "104", "exam_name": "104年第一次專技醫師中醫師分階段考試、中醫師營養師心理師護理師社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 24, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02549', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-104-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '機構對不適任員工，實施矯正行動過程之後，決定終止聘僱。主管與此類非志願離職的員工進行離職面 談的重心應優先放在下列何者？', '["檢視員工過去的缺失", "告知解僱決定和辦理離職程序", "提供未來生涯規劃之建議", "介紹新工作"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:13+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7528bca53179", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6a2111ca5bab", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "104030", "c": "110", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "104", "exam_name": "104年第一次專技醫師中醫師分階段考試、中醫師營養師心理師護理師社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 25, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02550', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-104-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '新管理主義可能造成工作條件惡化，導致員工多樣化的職場抗拒。因此，批判管理研究（critical management studies）的倡導者Alvesson & Willmott主張：不期待組織在短期內進行重大改變，而應逐步降低組織對員 工的限制，讓員工有更高的自主性。這種主張最適合稱為下列何者？', '["社會改革（social reform）", "意識覺醒（conscious awareness）", "微型解放（micro-emancipation）", "製造甘願（manufacturing consent）"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:13+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7528bca53179", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6a2111ca5bab", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "104030", "c": "110", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "104", "exam_name": "104年第一次專技醫師中醫師分階段考試、中醫師營養師心理師護理師社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 26, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL)
